        "description": "<p><em>Disco Fever</em> is a single-screen action game where the player takes control of a DJ. The screens shows a night club as well as alleys leading to a record store. At the club, the character's girlfriend is sitting at a table and the main objective is to buy her drinks. This is done by first moving to the bar and then to her table. For every drink he buys twenty points are earned. At the same time the DJ must keep the disco going and therefore he has make his way through the alleys, reach the record store and return to the turntable with a new record. A timer will count down and when it reaches zero a life is lost. It is also necessary to avoid the muggers that stalk the alleys since any contact with them will also takes away a life. For every record played more dancers will occupy the dance floor, making it harder to find a path through.</p>",
