        "description": "<p><i>Pac Mr</i> (sic) is a clone of Pac-Man for the Mattel Aquarius. The player takes control of a character in a maze with the goal of eating all of the dots and avoiding the spaceships. Once the player consumes a big, red circle, the tables are turned, with the player being able to temporarily eat the spaceships. There are 4 lives, and the game ends when they are all gone.</p>",
        "genres": [
            {
